---
import { GOOGLE_BUSINESS_REVIEWS_URL } from '../data/site';
import { GOOGLE_REVIEW_HIGHLIGHTS } from '../data/googleReviews';

const hasHighlights = GOOGLE_REVIEW_HIGHLIGHTS.length > 0;
---

<section id="opinie" class="py-14 md:py-18 bg-gray-50 border-y border-gray-100">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-8 md:mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 text-brand-carmine mb-4" aria-hidden="true">
        <i data-lucide="star" class="fill-current w-6 h-6"></i>
        <i data-lucide="star" class="fill-current w-6 h-6"></i>
        <i data-lucide="star" class="fill-current w-6 h-6"></i>
        <i data-lucide="star" class="fill-current w-6 h-6"></i>
        <i data-lucide="star" class="fill-current w-6 h-6"></i>
      </div>
      <h2 class="cinzel text-3xl md:text-4xl text-brand-steel mb-4">Opinie rodziców i pacjentów</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] text-gray-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
        Poniżej wybrane cytaty z opinii w Google Maps. Pełną, aktualną listę zawsze znajdziesz na wizytówce gabinetu.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-10">
        <a
          href={GOOGLE_BUSINESS_REVIEWS_URL}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-brand-steel/15 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-steel shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-brand-carmine hover:text-brand-carmine"
        >
          <i data-lucide="external-link" class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          Wszystkie opinie w Google
        </a>
      </div>

      {hasHighlights ? (
        <ul class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8 list-none p-0 m-0">
          {GOOGLE_REVIEW_HIGHLIGHTS.map((review) => (
            <li>
              <blockquote class="h-full rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm flex flex-col">
                <div class="flex gap-0.5 text-brand-carmine mb-3" aria-label={`Ocena ${review.rating} z 5`}>
                  {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map((n) => (
                    <i
                      data-lucide="star"
                      class:list={[
                        'w-4 h-4 shrink-0 fill-current',
                        n <= review.rating ? 'text-brand-carmine' : 'text-gray-200',
                      ]}
                    />
                  ))}
                </div>
                <p class="text-[15px] text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-4">„{review.text}”</p>
                <footer class="text-xs text-gray-400 border-t border-gray-50 pt-4 flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2">
                  <cite class="not-italic font-semibold text-brand-steel">{review.authorLabel}</cite>
                  {review.timeLabel && <span>{review.timeLabel}</span>}
                  <span class="w-full text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 mt-1">Opinia z Google Maps</span>
                </footer>
              </blockquote>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      ) : (
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-gray-200 bg-white/80 px-6 py-12 text-center max-w-xl mx-auto"
          role="status"
        >
          <p class="text-[15px] text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Brak opinii w danych — dodaj wpisy w <code class="text-xs bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-brand-steel">src/data/googleReviews.ts</code>.
            Pełną listę w Google zobaczysz po kliknięciu powyżej.
          </p>
          <a
            href={GOOGLE_BUSINESS_REVIEWS_URL}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-carmine hover:text-brand-steel transition-colors"
          >
            Przejdź do opinii w Google
            <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      )}

      <p class="mt-8 text-center text-[11px] text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Pełna lista i aktualne oceny są zawsze w Google — na stronie pokazujemy wybrane cytaty zgodnie z treścią wizytówki.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
      <a
        href="#kontakt"
        class="btn-gold inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider"
      >
        Umów wizytę dla dziecka
        <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
